# Teddy's Wealthome - Real Estate Website

A modern, responsive real estate landing page designed to showcase property listings, highlight renovation services, and feature customer testimonials. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

![Wealthome Preview](./assets/images/hero-preview.png)

## рџЏ  Features

- **Responsive Design** вЂ“ Works seamlessly on mobile, tablet, and desktop.
- **Interactive Search Bar** вЂ“ Filter by buy/sell/rent, property type, and location.
- **Property Cards** вЂ“ Display image, price, address, and key details (beds, baths, sqft).
- **Favorite Button** вЂ“ Click the heart icon to save favorite listings (UI toggle).
- **Feature Sections** вЂ“ Highlight renovation specialties with icon lists.
- **Video Section** вЂ“ Placeholder for a promotional video with animated play button.
- **Customer Stories** вЂ“ Testimonials with star ratings and avatars.
- **Sticky Header** вЂ“ Changes background on scroll for better visibility.
- **Mobile Navigation** вЂ“ Collapsible hamburger menu for small screens.
- **Smooth Scroll** вЂ“ For internal anchor links.

## рџ› пёЏ Technologies Used

- **HTML5** вЂ“ Semantic markup
- **CSS3** вЂ“ Custom properties, Flexbox, Grid, Animations
- **JavaScript (ES6)** вЂ“ DOM manipulation, event handling, scroll effects
- **Google Fonts** вЂ“ Montserrat font family
- **Google Material Symbols** вЂ“ Icon library

