## рџљЂ How to Run

1. **Clone or download** this repository to your local machine.
2. Make sure all files and folders maintain the structure shown above.
3. Open `index.html` in any modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge).
4. No server or build tools required вЂ“ it's a static website.

## рџЋЁ Customization

### Changing Content

- **Property Cards** вЂ“ Edit the HTML inside `.property-list` to update images, prices, and details.
- **Customer Names** вЂ“ Replace the `<h3>` text inside `.story-card` elements.
- **Feature Texts** вЂ“ Modify the paragraphs and list items in the `#FEATURE` sections.
- **Footer Info** вЂ“ Update contact email, address, and social media links.

### Styling

- All colors, fonts, and spacing are defined in `assets/css/style.css` using CSS custom properties (`:root`). Change values there for global updates.

### Images

- Replace images in `assets/images/` with your own (keep the same filenames or update `src` in HTML).

## рџ“„ JavaScript Functionality

| Feature          | Description                                                  |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Mobile Menu      | Toggles `.active` class on navbar and hamburger icon.        |
| Header Scroll    | Adds background when scrolled >50px.                         |
| Favorite Buttons | Toggle `active` class on heart icons (event delegation).     |
| Smooth Scroll    | Enables smooth scrolling for anchor links starting with `#`. |

